  "description": "Wide-coverage suite spanning every entity: Tickets, TicketComments, Bills, Customers, Users, Roles, Departments, Regions, Countries, Outages, MeterReadings, CSAT, Tariffs, plus lookups (ServiceType, ComplaintType, ResolutionType, TicketCategory hierarchy, TicketStatus, TicketPriority, TicketSource, AI analyses). Shapes: COUNT, filtered SELECT, projection, ORDER BY, TOP-N, SUM/AVG/MIN/MAX, GROUP BY (1+ multi-dim), HAVING, 1/2/3-hop joins, EXISTS/NOT EXISTS, IN, BETWEEN, LIKE keyword search, hierarchy walking (parent/child), temporal ranges, pattern-discovery, multi-step temporal comparisons, bilingual Arabic, refusal/safety. ~150 questions — runs via the general schema + semantic-layer path (not ticket-only embeddings).",
